The paper discusses a new approach to supervised embedding models for ranking, recommendation, and annotation tasks. These tasks are commonly associated with information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
